                <h1>RICHER LIFE BAROMETER</h1>
                <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-7 col-sm-8">
                    <p>
                    This questionnaire looks at what is important to you in life. Although we all have many goals in life, the format of this questionnaire encourages you to prioritise what is more important to you as an individual.
                    <br/><br/>You will be presented with a series of pairs as shown below</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row px-5">
                <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-9 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">

