                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row p-5">
                <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-7 col-sm-8">
                <p>For each pair use the slider to indicate which option better reflects you.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="px-5 pb-5 hidden-lg hidden-md visible-sm visible-xs">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                        <div class="p-2 nextPrev">
